      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">19 August 1860. ¶ My dear Krichauff, ¶  ¶ Today I received a cheque from the Colonial Bank ¶  ¶ that ¶  ¶ you were so kind ¶  ¶ as ¶  ¶ to remit to me through this institution. ¶  ¶  ¶ Could you pleas...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">60.08.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Friedrich Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">19/8/60.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mein lieber Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Heute erhielt ich von der Colonial Bank eine Anweisung, welche Du durch diese Anstalt mir zu übersenden die Güte hattest.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Möchtest Du so freundlich sein mir mitzutheilen, ob diese Summe von Freund Fischer kommt oder ob selbige ein anderer Erlös ist.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bin eifrig daran, den ersten Band der Flora dieser Colonie zu beenden, so dass ich nur flüchtig schreibe. Das Werk soll Dir gesandt werden, — ich denke um Weihnacht, bis wann ich den Band zu vollenden hoffe. Wieviel Arbeit gehört doch dazu, wenn man etwas critisch Richtiges u genau Beobachtetes produciren will.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe noch kaum Hand an die Inspection Deines Herbar gelegt, obwohl ich es hin u wieder benutzte. Das Meiste, was es enthält, wäre mir für unsere Sammlung willkommen</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich glaube schon einmal vorgefragt zu haben, ob Du es mir nicht in toto überlassen möchtest, wenn ich Dir eine Sammlung Australischer Pflanzen sende, die doch in diesem Lande das Nothwendigste für den Botaniker ist.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoffend dass Ihr Euch alle wohl befindet,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">verbleibe ich Dein</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dich hochschätzender<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Freund</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">19 August 1860.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Krichauff,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Today I received a cheque from the Colonial Bank<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>you were so kind<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to remit to me through this institution.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Could you please tell me<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>whether this amount comes from our friend Fischer,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ludwig Fischer.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or whether it is from some other proceeds.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am kept busy<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>finishing the first volume of the flora of this colony,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B62.03.03.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>so I only write in haste. The work will be sent to you, I think around Christmas, by which time I hope to complete the volume. How much labour is involved, if one wants to produce something critically correct and precisely observed.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have barely made a start with the inspection of your herbarium, although I have used it now and then.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Most of what it contains would be a welcome to me for our collection.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I believe I have made some preliminary enquiries once before, whether you would not let me have it as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a whole<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>if I send you a collection of Australian plants in return, which is, after all, what is most needful<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for a botanist in this country.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Krichauff's donation of his 'general herbarium of several thousands well preserved plants' was reported in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to J. O'Shanassy, 10 March 1862. Not all these specimens have been indexed in AVH (accessed 14 August 2023). Most of them,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>collected in 1847 and earlier, are from cultivated plants,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>recorded as from ‘Ex hort. Kilins’ [from Botanic Garden Kiel], or 'Ex horto bot Berolinensi [from Botanic Garden Berlin]; some are evidently from the University botanic garden, Leipzig.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Not all are indigenous to Europe; there are examples of species from North America, Asia, and Australia, and widely cultivated crops of uncertain origin.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoping you are all well,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I remain with great esteem</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your friend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
